caller_intent: Jena from Alliance Insurance is contacting Calvin to review his policy renewal and confirm details, requesting a callback for further discussion.
resolution_steps: Jena greets Calvin and introduces herself as an Alliance Insurance agent.
She mentions she is reaching out to review his policy renewal and ensure accuracy.
Calvin responds that he is in the middle of a job and agrees to call back at his convenience.
Jena thanks him and ends the call.
summary: Jena from Alliance Insurance contacted Calvin to discuss his upcoming policy renewal, confirming the need for a callback to finalize details. Calvin agreed to reach out later, resulting in a successful arrangement for follow-up.
